WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:09.507
This week on <i> Vice,</i>

00:09.609 --> 00:12.943
the water crisis that's poisoning
the people of Flint, Michigan.

00:13.046 --> 00:14.512
All:
Flint lives matter!

00:17.884 --> 00:21.752
People are dying.
Who want to be next? Not me.

00:21.855 --> 00:24.722
So this is the Flint
Water Treatment Facility,

00:24.824 --> 00:27.959
which is where they failed to
treat the water for corrosion,

00:28.061 --> 00:29.995
which led to the entire lead crisis.

00:30.097 --> 00:31.796
It's all right.

